title: Mountain - Live - The Road Goes Ever On (1972) [FLAC]
description:
tracklist:

    1 - "Long Red" (West/Pappalardi/Ventura/Landsberg) - 5:44
    2 - "Waiting to Take You Away" (West) - 4:40
